OL,3,CGlyndwr National Park plans face
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry
OL,6,FPlans to create Wales' fourth national
OL,7,Fpark in north east Wales will be
OL,8,Freviewed at a public inquiry, the
OL,9,FWelsh Government has announced.
OL,11,FIt follows widespread opposition from
OL,12,Flocal authorities within the area
OL,13,Fcovered by the proposed park, and with
OL,14,Fconcerns over funding levels,
OL,15,Frestrictions on businesses and rising
OL,16,Fhouse prices.
OL,18,FCreating the Glyndwr national park was
OL,19,Fa commitment the Welsh Government made
OL,20,Ffor this Senedd term.
OL,26,@kD@Fs{
