OL,3,CGlyndwr National Park plans face
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister Huw Irranca
OL,7,FDavies MS, who is also Cabinet
OL,8,FSecretary for Climate Change & Rural
OL,9,FAffairs, said Wales' existing national
OL,10,Fparks contribute approximately #1
OL,11,Fbillion to the Welsh economy.
OL,13,F"I understand the concerns and
OL,14,Freservations that Local Authorities
OL,15,Fand other stakeholders have about the
OL,16,Festablishment of a new National Park
OL,17,Fand new National Park Authority" he
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@kD@Fs{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
