OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774559156
OL,3,CGlyndwr National Park plans face
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry
OL,6,F"It is a big change ` deliberately so,
OL,7,Fas it is designed to have a
OL,8,Fsignificant positive impact on our
OL,9,Fnatural environment and people's
OL,10,Fability to enjoy it. Consequently, it
OL,11,Fis right that these issues are
OL,12,Fconsidered very carefully."
OL,14,FGareth Ludkin, Policy Manager at
OL,15,FCampaign for National Parks, said:
OL,26,@kD@Fs{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774559156
OL,3,CGlyndwr National Park plans face
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry
OL,6,F"The consultation process clearly left
OL,7,Fquestions unanswered for Local
OL,8,FAuthorities and we are pleased to see
OL,9,Fa public inquiry announced. An inquiry
OL,10,Fof this type is a pretty typical
OL,11,Fprocess for new National Parks to go
OL,12,Fthrough, so it is essential that the
OL,13,Fnext Welsh Government conducts this
OL,14,Fconsultation in a thorough and timely
OL,15,Fmanner to allow a final decision to be
OL,16,Fmade on the National Park."
OL,26,@kD@Fs{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774559156
OL,3,CGlyndwr National Park plans face
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry
OL,6,F"It has been encouraging to see that
OL,7,Fat least 66% of people consulted
OL,8,Fshowed at least conditional support
OL,9,Ffor the proposed National Park. We
OL,10,Fthink a future Welsh Government has an
OL,11,Fopportunity here to be bold and
OL,12,Fcreative with this new opportunity,
OL,13,Festablishing an exemplar National Park
OL,14,Ffit for the 21st century and future
OL,15,Fgenerations."
OL,26,@kD@Fs{
