OL,3,CGlyndwr National Park plans face
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry
OL,6,FThough the Welsh Government says work
OL,7,Fwill now begin on established the
OL,8,F"public local inquiry", the imminent
OL,9,Fend of the Senedd term means any
OL,10,Fdecision to proceed with the park will
OL,11,Fbe taken by the next Welsh Government.
